erlang-kafka (1.1.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * implement high level asynchronous consumer
  * add module for simple wrappers
  * _socket: add extra tracing
  * macros: add missing 1 ErrorCode
  * add human readable mapping for error codes
  * codec: allow Kafka "string" to be Erlang binary()
  * add metadata/1 convenient wrapper in the main module
  * define some commonly used data types
  * _socket: add new option - sync_start
  * _socket: minor fix - add missing "behaviour" module option
  * _socket: implement {state_listener,X} option
  * deb specs: run unit tests during DEB package build
  * deb specs: pack header files in erlang-kafka-dev DEB package
  * deb specs: minor description fix

 -- Aleksey Morarash <aleksey.morarash@gmail.com>  Tue, 05 Apr 2016 15:58:41 +0300

